    "description": "<p>Hsieh Kun Co., Ltd. was founded in July 1997. For several years, it has been committed to the manufacturing of foundations, high-rigidity anti-vibration platforms, machine tool SEISMIC, EQE anti-vibration and anti-slip fixing, as well as raised floor cutting, aluminum extrusion, and stainless steel product design and development. In order to serve more manufacturers, an office was established in Tainan in August 2000, with Hsinchu as the headquarters. In view of future market changes, in July 2001, in order to expand its business, a factory was set up in Shanghai, China (Hsieh Wei Integrated Circuit Equipment (Shanghai) Co., Ltd.).</p>",
